{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">练习使用多用电表测电阻。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">欧姆定律。</span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">多用电表、电阻</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．机械调零：旋动定位螺丝使指针指在左端电流零刻度处，并将红、黑表笔分别接入</span>&ldquo;<span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">+</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">&rdquo;、&ldquo;</span>-&rdquo;插孔；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．选挡：选择开关置于欧姆表&ldquo;</span>&times;1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">&rdquo;挡；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．短接调零：在表笔短接时调整欧姆挡的调零旋钮使指针指在右端电阻零刻度处；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">4<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．测量读数：将红黑表笔搭接在待测电阻两端，读出指示的电阻值；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">5<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．改变电阻阻值，重复以上</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">过程；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">6<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．多用电表用完后，将选择开关置于&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">OFF</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">&rdquo;挡或交变电压的最高挡，拔出表笔。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">使用万用表测电阻读数时应将指针示数乘以挡位倍率</span></span></span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．测量时手不要接触表笔的金属部分；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">．合理选择量程，使指针尽可能指在中间刻度附近（若指针偏角太大，应改换低挡位；若指针偏角太小，应改换高挡位。每次换挡后均要重新短接调零。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}